OL,3,CPatients feel abandoned by 'broken'
OL,4,CGreater Manchester mental health care
OL,6,FPatients and staff at a Greater
OL,7,FManchester mental health service have
OL,8,Ftold ITV Granada the service is
OL,9,Fbroken, with those who need support
OL,10,Ffeeling 'abandoned'.
OL,12,FIt can be revealed that there are
OL,13,Fcurrently more than 500 people with
OL,14,Fsevere mental health issues waiting on
OL,15,Fa list and not receiving the help they
OL,16,Fneed. And even when they are seen,
OL,17,Fpatients say they're only offered
OL,18,Fshort-term fixes, with no ongoing
OL,19,Fsupport.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/15
