OL,3,CPatients feel abandoned by 'broken'
OL,4,CGreater Manchester mental health care
OL,6,FA doctor has described the services as
OL,7,F'unsafe', and says the public should
OL,8,Fbe alarmed.
OL,10,FOne patient, who we're calling Lisa to
OL,11,Fprotect her identity, says she's
OL,12,F'living a smaller life' because of her
OL,13,Flack of support from the service.
OL,15,F'Lisa' has had in-person support for
OL,16,Fthe last 25 years but has recently
OL,17,Fbeen discharged from the waiting well
OL,18,Fservice.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/15
