OL,3,CPatients feel abandoned by 'broken'
OL,4,CGreater Manchester mental health care
OL,6,F"To be provided with no service
OL,7,Foutside of a crises is abandoning us",
OL,8,Fshe said.
OL,10,F"We are the people who aren't going to
OL,11,Fget better.
OL,13,F"I had no plan, no prospect of more
OL,14,Fhelp, it seemed very basic and like
OL,15,Fthey were concerned whether I would
OL,16,Fcause a problem for them, IE,
OL,17,Ftriggering an inquest if I killed
OL,18,Fmyself.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/15
