OL,3,CPatients feel abandoned by 'broken'
OL,4,CGreater Manchester mental health care
OL,6,F"I'm terrified of becoming unwell
OL,7,Fagain which I know is inevitable. I'm
OL,8,Fnot stable. Nobody cares, and even if
OL,9,Fthey do care, they can't help."
OL,11,FDr John Mulligan, a Unite
OL,12,Frepresentative and Psychologist who
OL,13,Fworks in the Early Intervention
OL,14,FService, says he believes the system
OL,15,Fis broken.
OL,17,F"If your family member becomes unwell,
OL,18,Fyou're very unfortunate living in
OL,19,FManchester", he said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/15
