OL,3,CPatients feel abandoned by 'broken'
OL,4,CGreater Manchester mental health care
OL,6,F"The ratio of staff to service users
OL,7,Fis appalling in Manchester, so much so
OL,8,Fthat it's an abusive system we're in
OL,9,Fat the moment where people are not
OL,10,Fgetting what they need but there is a
OL,11,Fbit of a pattern or a repetitive cycle
OL,12,Fwhere some of our service users can't
OL,13,Feven talk about positives in their
OL,14,Fweek, they can't even talk about
OL,15,Frecovery and things that are going
OL,16,Fwell because they're afraid of being
OL,17,Fdischarged."
