OL,4,CGreater Manchester mental health care
OL,6,FOn Monday, early intervention mental
OL,7,Fhealth workers in Greater Manchester
OL,8,Fwent on strike for 24 hours, they say
OL,9,Fpoor staffing levels and lack of
OL,10,Ffunding is putting lives at risk.
OL,12,FA worry for Unite members is the
OL,13,Funallocated list, also known as the
OL,14,Fwaiting well list.
OL,16,FThere are 550 people with severe and
OL,17,Fenduring mental health issues on this
OL,18,Flist not currently receiving proper
OL,19,Fsupport.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/15
