OL,3,CPatients feel abandoned by 'broken'
OL,4,CGreater Manchester mental health care
OL,6,FMany of those discharged have been
OL,7,Fleft to fend for themselves.
OL,9,FAnnabel Marsh, a retired community
OL,10,Fmental health nurse, runs a support
OL,11,Fgroup and has been a lifeline for many.
OL,13,FShe says things have changed
OL,14,Fdrastically over the years.
OL,16,F"People are being neglected and
OL,17,Fabandoned because they have long-term
OL,18,Fissues and no voice and when you try
OL,19,Fand access help, there's nobody to try
OL,20,Fand give that help because the teams
OL,21,Fare overstretched and understaffed."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/15
