OL,6,FCraig has complex mental health issues
OL,7,Fand has been in and out of services
OL,8,Ffor nearly 30 years.
OL,10,FWhen he was first diagnosed it took
OL,11,Fweeks for him to get a designated
OL,12,Fworker, with his latest relapse it's
OL,13,Ftaken 5 years, in that time, he says
OL,14,Fthat he's lost everything.
OL,16,FCraig said: "My health degraded slowly
OL,17,Fand surely and my fears of why I was
OL,18,Ftrying to get help became more
OL,19,Fapparent.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/15
