OL,6,F"I struggled more with my own business
OL,7,Fthat I'd managed to build up with my
OL,8,Fwife. Then it moved to me not being
OL,9,Fable to work, then the psychosis
OL,10,Fdropped and that was me, I hardly left
OL,11,Fmy room for a year.
OL,13,F"If it had been ten years ago it might
OL,14,Fhave been different."
