OL,6,FResponding to the claims, Professor
OL,7,FManisha Kumar, chief medical officer
OL,8,Ffor NHS Greater Manchester, said:
OL,9,F"Mental health services in Greater
OL,10,FManchester, as across many parts of
OL,11,Fthe country, are facing significant
OL,12,Fpressures, especially as demand for
OL,13,Fservices has grown. Our mental health
OL,14,Fprofessionals continue to demonstrate
OL,15,Fincredible dedication and resilience
OL,16,Fin the face of these challenges.
