OL,4,CGreater Manchester mental health care
OL,6,F"We are focusing on preventing mental
OL,7,Fhealth problems and supporting good
OL,8,Fmental health, improving community
OL,9,Fservices, and strengthening our crisis
OL,10,Fresponse services to avoid admission
OL,11,Fwhere appropriate. We are working with
OL,12,Fpartners across the wider NHS, local
OL,13,Fauthorities, housing providers and the
OL,14,Fvoluntary sector to ensure people can
OL,15,Freceive the right care and support
OL,16,Fnear to where they live.
