OL,4,CGreater Manchester mental health care
OL,6,F"We are fully aware that some
OL,7,Findividuals are struggling to access
OL,8,Ftimely and appropriate support, and
OL,9,Fthis is an area that requires urgent
OL,10,Fattention. The impact of rising demand
OL,11,Ffor services has contributed to
OL,12,Fdifficulties in providing the level of
OL,13,Fcare that people need. We are
OL,14,Fcommitted to working with our partners
OL,15,Fin health and social care to develop
OL,16,Fsolutions that ensure more timely,
OL,17,Feffective support for individuals with
OL,18,Fserious mental health conditions.
